1. This project needs Java 1.8
2. Used Hipster library to find shortest Nodes, i tweaked some code of it to inject vertex dynamically.
    But i have seen one issue with this library, when entry point is second node in conveyor system 
    it is not returning results properly.
3. You can run App.java to test application.
4. Created three beans to represent the three Sections, conveyor system, departures and Bags.
5. I have created sample data using three text files and read the same in SampleData java file.
6. Created One test class  BaggageRouteServiceTest to test the functionality .
